{"tid":329713,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉］書展推介書籍","createTime":"2017-07-20T14:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T02:28:20.000Z","uid":109082,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"188cde0fcc43a6ee4394a52077418b929849a44f","tid":329713,"uid":109082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T14:51:42.000Z","msg":"小妹雖然未去，但就託左朋友買左兩本。<br />\n<br />\n一本係眾新聞出版的《1997年我們是記者》，入面收錄左22個前線記者的故仔，圖片和史料。好似：97大事紀、當時的報章頭條；回歸儀式上中英相方演辭。對於我呢d回歸時得幾歲的人，呢本書都得意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/224851_c08f1651c6de81d3b9e1da51a641b1d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F224851_c08f1651c6de81d3b9e1da51a641b1d9.jpg&h=b204de5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/225139_1f96a4cc0abf35436e05f45299afd6da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F225139_1f96a4cc0abf35436e05f45299afd6da.jpg&h=6c69f89c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲weekend會去行書展呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如開心share下有咩心水書籍呀。"},{"pid":"eb9fe8f33b3c59fe6de287a4c4874e30a32b7bbd","tid":329713,"uid":42982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T14:56:13.000Z","msg":"在乎"},{"pid":"93d349c0fb5b9752fe592aa6dc620a0a958fa6a4","tid":329713,"uid":1643,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T15:18:03.000Z","msg":"今年書展痴撚線，無國界、宣明會、渣打呢 d 完全唔關書事、仲有大部份都係賣旅行書，雖然主題係旅遊都唔使咁撚多丫&hellip;"},{"pid":"a8404dda8a29e77d43e06b08b4cdc2a004e345a8","tid":329713,"uid":71122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T15:43:53.000Z","msg":"我聽日去書展，但係我睇嗰啲書好偏門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68211075eda777f4119db951862e28220731c73","tid":329713,"uid":26314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2