/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70875392556e2c71fcf2448e4796f11899a473a2","tid":329713,"uid":62842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:06:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知多唔多外文金融書呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n同問"},{"pid":"47b3ea99530374d479bbc5eb6a6b9831db61a55b","tid":329713,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今年個書展好撚無聊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用旅遊做題真係好廢，同埋冇咩好突出的新書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29b48bcded23084b2877230ea0a2d198368e301","tid":329713,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:12:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08a97e0605ce13c02343ee48fc17fb10de4d6b69","tid":329713,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:29:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個年代 仲邊有人睇書 求知識既上網都搵到晒仲要最新   書冇得更新</blockquote><br />\n上一代人好多都仲係鍾意睇書<br />\n<br />\n同埋 書係比較有系統咁講知識<br />\n易d跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21973b38cb0da7c0835479f46e1e3bb688a5d4c1","tid":329713,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:38:49.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好買志文出版社 新潮文庫。。。。"},{"pid":"187584044954131299c9e7d79e729474c71ec001","tid":329713,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:41:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>千祈唔好買志文出版社 新潮文庫。。。。</blockquote><br />\nwhy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da63226f715f936e59ad6193e0952b9c56afccd8","tid":329713,"uid":37081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:43:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會係入面再揀<br />\n<br />\n- [ ] <span style=\"color: red;\">獨立屠場 - 盧斯達：明報出版社 - 1C-C04-16</span><br />\n- [ ] 屹屹屹 - 仇思達：明報出版社 - 1C-C04-16<br />\n- [ ] 絕 3 - 有心無默：點子出版 1A-B16<br />\n- [ ] 小王子廣東話版：田園書屋 1B-B02 $78 8折<br />\n- [ ] 社工書：城市大學出版社<br />\n- [ ] <span style=\"color: red;\">有冇人熱烈慶祝香港回歸祖國二十年</span><br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇：<br />\n- [ ] 鬱躁的城邦：香港民族源流史：紅出版 (圓桌文化) （要搵）<br />\n- [ ] 香港獨立論（要搵）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果想買鬱躁的城邦，可以買台灣版香港，鬱躁的家邦：本土觀點的香港源流史，左岸出係讀者共和國有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n準備買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152723258786a2d65a35001e4d30df427975d663","tid":329713,"uid":42429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:45:47.000Z","msg":"買左天地堆散文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1bd878efe210e1231970852269b87d1ca4db085","tid":329713,"uid":117868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:47:03.000Z","msg":"第一次覺得行書展會悶<br />\n之前由朝行到黑<br />\n今日行左唔知有冇兩個鐘就走"},{"pid":"61c8101e430e536ab13da503aa851756cbf958fa","tid":329713,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T16:22:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7acbd85035146be59e5579c3ec3e5a6ef4003fb","tid":329713,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T16:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢個年代 仲邊有人睇書 求知識既上網都搵到晒仲要最新   書冇得更新</blockquote><br />\n上一代人好多都仲係鍾意睇書<br />\n<br />\n同埋 書係比較有系統咁講知識<br />\n易d跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最慘係更新唔到呢 真心覺得跟住舊版書學影響好大</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好睇你買咩書，如係文史哲又冇話咩唔好，尤其係經典一類。另外，小說，文學類問題亦都唔會太大。<br />\n<br />\n如果係社科政經類就可能有少少問題。"},{"pid":"d6607f262017425365aa4f3ed0b82a6900a779b7","tid":329713,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔知多唔多外文金融書呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n同問</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有檔專賣大學textbook,有會計金融既仲要平"},{"pid":"1f0489304005a380530a023d422f283b5d27bcb2","tid":329713,"uid":63328,"like"